        "text": "Hey everyone! I'm Matyas from Hungary. Been listening to the podcast for a couple years now, but what finally nudged me into joining the FoC slack was recommending my choice of iOS guitar tuner, which is <https:\/\/apps.apple.com\/us\/app\/tonalenergy-tuner-metronome\/id497716362|TonalEnergy>\n\nAfter a 12-year career as a frontend dev, I barely have any _good_ _feelings of computing_ these days, but listening to the podcast seems to help.\n\nOutside of work, I make music with my band, and I try to pour whatever creative energy I have left into writing stories for games – optimistically hoping that one day I might not only finish one, but actually develop it too.",
