        "client_msg_id": "1FAD428B-BB6F-41F3-AFF2-BCB977E88CFE",
        "text": "Hi all! I'm Pontus from Sweden and I found my way here through Ink &amp; Switch and (I think) <https:\/\/youtu.be\/0yKf8TrLUOw?is=pzXeyigQNI_PVKWf|a talk about Programming in Excel by Felinne Hermans>. \nI'm interested in how technology shapes our lives, online culture, end-user programming, and being creative with computers in general. \n\nSince my first interaction with a computer I've wanted to master them, knowing it all. But it was not until recently I made it my main occupation as a specialist in product information management (ETL with csv-files and Miller ftw!).\n\nMy fascination range from <https:\/\/truth-and-beauty.net\/|Moritz Stefaner> to <applewebdata:\/\/9E2984CF-025E-47CD-8C9F-EC1A4D8C2310\/arm\/Raspberry%20Pi%20-%20FreeBSD%20Wiki|Raspberry Pi>, from <https:\/\/science-to-touch.com\/en\/iOrnament.html|iOrnament> to Ian Hacking, from Conway's Game of Life to the <https:\/\/www.explainxkcd.com\/wiki\/index.php\/3198:_Double-Pronged_Extension_Cord|Daemon Core>. ",
